author: antelder
msg: Don't use url for systemId as it fails when url is for a nested ear resource as the archive: protocol isn't known to woodstock url handler. As far as i can see we don't need the systemId for anything and the build is working fine without it

author: mjakl
msg: Introduced a new wrapper for the payload (PayloadItem) which stores the time we received the message and hence is used to return the list of items in a non-arbitrary ordering for disco#items (reversed chronological). Fixes VYSPER-84.
